- Right here.

96
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,256
I just stopped by the loft
to pick up your blue suit.

97
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,999
I figured you'd had enough
of green.

98
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,576
Hey, I made that green suit
work, though.

99
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,160
