and help support Cecile?

106
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,558
Yeah. When are they
coming back, by the way?

107
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,376
- They've been gone forever.
- Uh, he's not sure.

108
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,596
After having a psychopath
break into his home,

109
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,880
