115
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:49,149
Hey, you ready to get those
shards out of your hands?

116
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,276
Hell yes!

117
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,829
I haven't been able to play
PS4 properly for weeks.

118
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,639
See you in there.

119
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,560
Hey, you feel that?

120
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,756
