any invoices from you

124
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,990
in the near future.

125
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:07,080
<i>Oh, that's all right.</i>

126
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:11,195
This is one mystery
I will solve for free.

127
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:34,519
<i>The state versus
Joslyn Jackam,</i>

128
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:39,516
Criminal Court of Central City,
meta-crime number 99512.

129
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,717
Welcome back to my courtroom,
Miss Horton.

130
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:45,157
