was enjoyable?

131
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,600
Thank you, Your Honor.

132
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:49,275
I am very happy
to be back at work.

133
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:51,272
<i>Yeah, there never really is
enough time</i>

134
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,397
with a newborn, is there?

135
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:56,040
There is not.
You may proceed.

136
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,679
Thank you, Your Honor.

137
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,634
The prosecution
intends to prove

138
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,439
that between November 20th
and 27th,

139
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:05,160
Joslyn Jackam
used this device,

140
