144
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,911
<i>massive property damage
at Iron Heights,</i>

145
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,957
<i>the grounding
of 21 separate flights</i>

146
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,156
<i>at Sheldon County Airport,</i>

147
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,277
<i>and the attempted murder</i>

148
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:23,916
of her own father,
Mark Mardon.

149
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,310
Now, this attack
on her father was...

150
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,637
Uh...

151
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:35,189
Uh, the...

152
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:37,715
the attack on her father
was premeditated.

153
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,952
Um, and...

154
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,555
the prosecution
is seeking the...

