00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,597
Are you okay?

156
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,677
Uh...

157
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,597
yeah, it's just a...

158
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,114
feeling.

159
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,949
I'll be fine.

160
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:08,559
The prosecution is seeking the
maximum sentence, Your Honor.

161
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,160
<i>Gotcha.</i>

162
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,309
All right, almost done.

163
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:20,631
Micro-scale surgery
is not the easiest.

164
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,376
Is that why you missed these
the first time?

165
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,400
Hey, now!

166
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,114
All right, there you go.

167
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:28,510
Your hands are officially
dagger shard free.

168
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,600
Hallelu.

169
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,716
One more thing.

170
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:43,195
Mm, meta-sutures
for meta-wounds,

171
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,555
that's clever.

172
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:47,235
Ah! Note to self,
ice healing actually hurts.

173
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,760
Don't be a wuss.

174
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:52,712
Wuss.
You're the wuss.

175
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,632
Looks like you've got
this whole

176
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,279
Caitlyn/Killer Frost thing
down pat.

177
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,999
- Eh, not totally.
- I got it.

178
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,351
