sans Vibe-age, you know?

187
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:23,194
And not having villains
breathing down my neck

188
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:25,749
once a week, I have to say,
is pretty schway.

189
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,399
Well, if we're gonna
defeat Cicada,

190
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,119
we need
a fully functioning Vibe.

191
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,510
So hopefully
this does the trick.

192
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,273
Here, souvenirs.

193
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,955
- Oh, thank you so much.
- You're welcome.

