<i>Touch your nose.</i>

202
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,957
Hey! That's my car!

203
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,736
And then what happened,
Miss Pellett?

204
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:19,754
