of lightning tornado.

205
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,911
<i>I wasn't sure if any of us
were gonna make it.</i>

206
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,000
I got to go.

207
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:29,436
One moment, please.

208
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,272
I got to go.
There's been a car theft.

209
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,256
What are you talking about?
You're my lead CSI witness.

210
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:36,760
You're on the stand
in 30 minutes.

211
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,957
I'm sorry.
It's a Lamborghini, all right?

212
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:41,016
The cops aren't gonna be able
to keep up with this thing.

213
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:42,216
- It'll be quick.
- 30 minutes.

214
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,799
- All right.
<i>- Miss Horton?</i>

215
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,199
